  "3193560": {
    "name": "哎呀哎呀？房东呀！",
    "steam_appid": 3193560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>故事</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >父亲去世后，玩家举目无亲，只剩从父亲那里继承的公寓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为房东后，一名神秘青年突然出现在你眼前，如此警告。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;你家公寓房客里有‘妖怪’&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从那一天起，你的推理生活正式拉开了帷幕，你的任务是揭示那些巧妙伪装成人类的妖怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>概述</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《哎呀哎呀？房东呀！》是一款推理探险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏是一个包含多个章节的故事，当你进入下一章时，季节会发生变化，一些居民会被新的居民和迁入的幽灵以及在上一章中被驱逐的幽灵所取代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一章都要求玩家推断出混入的幽灵是谁，找到他们的证据并驱逐他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >影片的总主题是找出混入主人公公寓的妖怪的原因，以及告诉他们这些妖怪的神秘青年的意图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>本作特色</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras/cb8826bec8edb0d93bdd3802a9cc67f9.avif?t=1747028727\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras_big/cb8826bec8edb0d93bdd3802a9cc67f9.avif?t=1747028727 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与房客谈话，寻找化作房客的妖怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房客会跟成为房东的玩家抱怨、请求，或者单纯闲聊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些信息都能用来寻找妖怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感觉不对劲的对话，或许就是找出妖怪的线索。把重要的发言记下来吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>查看公寓监控 (出现在第二章）</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras/05dd40330bea134ce169690a8532ae3f.avif?t=1747028727\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras_big/05dd40330bea134ce169690a8532ae3f.avif?t=1747028727 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妖怪非常狡猾。就算安装监控，对方也不一定会现出原形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，四下无人时，妖怪可能会采取有别于人类的行动，或者做出平常假扮人类时不会做的事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乍看平平无奇的小举动，或许正是关键线索。盯紧每一个细节，找出真正的妖怪吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>找到妖怪就逐出公寓</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras/fe9388301dfb6d3a1d4a85a154b359aa.avif?t=1747028727\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras_big/fe9388301dfb6d3a1d4a85a154b359aa.avif?t=1747028727 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整理各种信息，锁定妖怪后，就将对方逐出公寓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras/b1996923ee75c7fec2b68d2f29a16d48.avif?t=1747028727\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras_big/b1996923ee75c7fec2b68d2f29a16d48.avif?t=1747028727 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，仅仅找出你认为是妖怪的房客，并不能让对方乖乖离开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还需要拿出证据，例如其他房客是人类的证明，才能说服妖怪坦白自己的真实身份。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果误将真正的人类当作妖怪赶走，剩下的房客就会更加疑神疑鬼。这正是妖怪想看到的局面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过细致地向房客打听消息，收集情报，并找出隐藏在其中的 “违和感” 线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经过无数次的推理思考，当你终于将 “妖怪” 逼入绝境的那一刻——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你一定会体验到只有这款游戏才能带来的成就感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>如果没在期限内赶走妖怪……</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras/41035c129790d1b648e6d649036a03b4.avif?t=1747028727\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193560/extras_big/41035c129790d1b648e6d649036a03b4.avif?t=1747028727 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妖怪会在新月之夜释放真正的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当那一刻到来，弱小的人类只能听天由命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是单纯的解谜，而是一个等待你来揭晓的悄然温暖心田的角色成长故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>游戏时间</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总游戏时间 <u>约为 10 小时</u>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您不习惯 “推理游戏” ，可能需要更长的时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您对本作的游戏内容感到好奇，我们建议您先玩 <u>免费试用版</u> 。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它包含教程元素，允许您玩到第一章结束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>视频发布准则</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于分销商，分销视频发布准则发布在官方网站上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请看一下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>适用于 Steam Deck 上的玩家</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请运行 “兼容性 - 质子”。</p>",
